/* 组件根节点占满父级宽度，确保跑马灯有完整可用宽度（弹窗内由父级 class 再控宽） */
:host {
  display: block;
}

/* ── 滚动公告 ── */
.notice-bar {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12rpx;
  padding: 16rpx 24rpx;
  margin-bottom: 20rpx;
  background: rgba(7, 193, 96, 0.08);
  border: 2rpx solid rgba(7, 193, 96, 0.18);
  border-radius: 16rpx;
}
.notice-icon {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  font-size: 26rpx;
}
.notice-viewport {
  flex: 1;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.notice-track {
  display: inline-block;
  white-space: nowrap;
  font-size: 24rpx;
  color: #1a8d4e;
  letter-spacing: 0.5rpx;
  padding-left: 100%;
  animation: notice-marquee 6s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes notice-marquee {
  0% { transform: translateX(0); }
  100% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
}
